    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with at two pounds of gemstones. Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine gemstones, as well as smaller tumbled stones, the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones awaits! HOW TO USE: Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (scoop and sifting screen not included); dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed! Clean and dry found gemstones and rocks and store in included burlap drawstring bag for safekeeping</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 5lb Rough Gemstone Paydirt Bag Gold Panning Kits (8 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with at two pounds of gemstones. Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine gemstones, as well as smaller tumbled stones, the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones awaits!</p>\n  <p>HOW TO USE: Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (scoop and sifting screen not included); dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed! Clean and dry found gemstones and rocks and store in included burlap drawstring bag for safekeeping</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>5LB GEMSTONE PAYDIRT:</strong> Enjoy the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones! Each five pound bag is packed with a rich assortment of genuine rough gemstones, (two pounds worth), as well an assortment of tumbled stones, all waiting to be discovered</li>\n    <li><strong>TOP QUALITY GEMSTONES:</strong> In your paydirt, you’ll discover an assortment of rough gemstones like Amazonite, Rough Amethyst, Carnelian, Citrine, Clear Quartz, Fuchsite, Labradorite, Pyrite, Moonstone, Rose Quartz, Sea Jasper, Smoky Quartz, Tiger Eye and more</li>\n    <li><strong>HOW TO USE:</strong> Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (not included), dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed; then use the gemstone identification chart to identify gemstones!</li>\n    <li><strong>ROCKS AND MINERALS COLLECTION:</strong> Perfect for hobbyists, rock collectors, and gold prospectors looking for a fun, hands on, outdoor activity</li>\n    <li><strong>IDENTIFICATION CHART:</strong> Double sided gemstone rocks and mineral collection identification chart and precious gemstone facts sheet makes identifying gemstones easy and fun</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/kit_lg_geodes_hammer_updated.jpg\" alt=\"Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with at two pounds of gemstones\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> PDB0005PARENT</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>In your gemstone paydirt, youâ ll discover an assortment of rough gemstones like Amazonite, Rough Amethyst, Carnelian, Citrine, Clear Quartz, Fuchsite, Labradorite, Pyrite, Moonstone, Rose Quartz, Sea Jasper, Smoky Quartz, Tiger Eye and more!</p>\n  <p>Use the gemstone identification chart to identify which gemstones you uncovered!</p>\n  <p>Whether you&#039;re a seasoned gem enthusiast or a curious beginner, our gemstone paydirt delivers the thrill of sifting through rich, organic material to uncover genuine gemstones. Perfect for hobbyists, rock collectors, and gold prospectors looking for a fun, hands on outdoor activity!</p>\n  <p>KIT INCLUDES: 5lb rough gemstone paydirt bag, 8 x 12 burlap cinch bag for rock and gemstone storage, paydirt screening instructions card and a double sided gemstone identification chart and information card</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
